{"tid":987903,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"想睇精神科 想問 流程係點 洗費係唔係好大","createTime":"2019-01-19T15:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T13:53:07.000Z","uid":123177,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"607456da1c268f0e7ead425ce28ee1503442a00c","tid":987903,"uid":123177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"近呢一年，發覺自己情緒都好唔穩定 。<br />\n經常突然極唔開心，冇精神，暴躁。<br />\n控制唔到自己發少d卑氣，同埋都有影響埋身邊既朋友<br />\n有時甚至想從此消失...<br />\n<br />\n工作是穩定的 當然有時會多野做<br />\n但更多係一件事，朋友冇心一句已經好強烈影響到我心情，<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢地都開始疏遠我。或者，留響身邊既 都可能唔頂得順我幾耐<br />\n<br />\n我想睇睇精神科 想問下 有咩流程？<br />\n同埋 如果要食藥 洗費大唔大 係唔係要食一世<br />\n<br />\n我只係想 好似以前咁 普普通通 開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5046fd4db8f6ec2289dc7f2d74c19467e2aedd","tid":987903,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T15:58:17.000Z","msg":"搵私家"},{"pid":"9e2af143309dc0e3b5a57361d084cfbf5c5de224","tid":987903,"uid":123177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b5046fd4db8f6ec2289dc7f2d74c19467e2aedd","tid":987903,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T15:58:17.000Z","msg":"搵私家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:01:29.000Z","msg":"等佢地再轉介？<br />\n通常精神科 一次睇幾錢？<br />\n<br />\n同埋 要睇幾多次先段到症？<br />\n藥貴唔貴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c34577002bf297a41caf0992a5d9d364e36160f","tid":987903,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e2af143309dc0e3b5a57361d084cfbf5c5de224","tid":987903,"uid":123177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b5046fd4db8f6ec2289dc7f2d74c19467e2aedd","tid":987903,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T15:58:17.000Z","msg":"搵私家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:01:29.000Z","msg":"等佢地再轉介？<br />\n通常精神科 一次睇幾錢？<br />\n<br />\n同埋 要睇幾多次先段到症？<br />\n藥貴唔貴？<img src=\"/asse